  "instructions": [
    "Heat the duck fat in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic and sauté until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the buckwheat groats and stir to coat with the fat and mix with the onion and garlic.",
    "Add the dates, cumin, and crushed red pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the salt and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10-12 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the parsley, ginger, and pistachios.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional parsley and pistachios if desired."
